org.universAAL.ucc.model.preferences

Class Preferences

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.universAAL.ucc.model.preferences.Preferences

  • public class Preferences
extends Object
    The preferences contains the setup information of uCC. It has a admin user with a password, a ip to access the uCC, an ip to communicate with the uStore and a language setting parameter.
    Author:
    Nicole Merkle
